{
  "stem": "26983.5",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he even succeeded to take out one prisoner, Lederer.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He smuggled him a-- a German uniform, and he took him out.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And this Lederer came later to Theresienstadt and told the people what's going on.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Auschwitz, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was one-- he came later on, back again.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He wanted to take this-- his-- this woman.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, he was denounced.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- in the German court.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he was killed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, he was a German SS.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But was a good one.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No. the woman-- as far as I know-- survived.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Anyhow, this Pestek had always all kinds of talks with Fredy Hirsch.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And if he came and had to talk to Fredy Hirsch, I had to be outside and have a good look-- that if Bundrok or other Germans come, I had to--",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--warn them.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because sometimes Mengele come.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Opposite was the-- krankenblock.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And Mengele came often to visit them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He came also to us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Midgets.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He-- he wanted gypsies and midgets.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Maybe there was one, but whoever was there, when Mengele took him, there was, I remember, two-- I mean two couples.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I remember one very well-- [NON-ENGLISH] brother.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But Mengele took them to his compound in the Zigeunerlager, where all the--",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--they were kept there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And later on I will tell you we visited this block.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I can tell you more about it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But now, with this kinderblock-- so we were guarding Pestek and-- with Fredy Hirsch, who had all kinds of talks.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there were rumors they are preparing here for a kind of uprising--",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--which didn't came through.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, which didn't happen.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And what happened, as I told you, on about the 6th of March, this--",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--the-- '44, this one group of people who came before us went to the other camp.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
